stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> OpenLoginPage
    OpenLoginPage --> EnterCredentials
    EnterCredentials --> SubmitLogin : POST /api/accounts/token/
    SubmitLogin --> ValidateCredentials
    ValidateCredentials --> InvalidCredentials : Wrong email/password
    InvalidCredentials --> EnterCredentials
    ValidateCredentials --> CheckSuspended
    CheckSuspended --> AccountSuspended : User is suspended
    AccountSuspended --> [*]
    CheckSuspended --> GenerateJWT : Account active
    GenerateJWT --> StoreTokens : Access + Refresh tokens
    StoreTokens --> RedirectDashboard
    RedirectDashboard --> UserSession
    UserSession --> ClickLogout
    ClickLogout --> ClearTokens
    ClearTokens --> RedirectLogin
    RedirectLogin --> [*]